#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cfeatures%5Crules-policy-parameters.md:3
msgid ""
"The editor implements the **Rules–Policy–Parameters (RPP)** architectural "
"pattern for structuring government business rule management. Three separate "
"tabs map to the three layers of this pattern, each visually distinguished by "
"colour and labelled with its RPP role."
msgstr ""

